00:29.208 --> 00:30.041
Hey.

00:30.541 --> 00:31.416
Excuse me.

00:32.750 --> 00:34.083
We're closing.

00:34.166 --> 00:36.000
I'm sorry, Mavi. We'll leave.

00:41.166 --> 00:43.125
Do you know every employee's name?

00:44.375 --> 00:47.208
We've all been coming here
for years after work.

00:47.291 --> 00:48.375
Everyone except you.

00:49.583 --> 00:51.541
You always have something better to do.

00:52.208 --> 00:53.333
Things change.

00:57.666 --> 00:58.708
One for the road.

00:59.916 --> 01:00.875
The road where?

01:01.708 --> 01:02.833
To your place.

01:12.208 --> 01:13.041
Fuck.

01:13.541 --> 01:16.125
When I see you at the hospital
in that uniform…

01:16.666 --> 01:17.500
Shut up.

01:29.375 --> 01:30.208
No.

01:32.958 --> 01:33.875
No.

01:33.958 --> 01:34.916
Lina, what's wrong?

01:35.416 --> 01:37.333
This isn't… This isn't it.

01:37.833 --> 01:38.833
Are you okay?

01:38.916 --> 01:39.916
I have to go, Julio.

01:41.958 --> 01:43.833
-Did I do something wrong?
-No.

01:44.333 --> 01:45.166
You sure?

01:48.041 --> 01:48.875
Fuck.

02:28.541 --> 02:32.166
There's so much I want to tell you

02:35.458 --> 02:36.291
Are you cold?

02:37.666 --> 02:38.750
I'm fine.

02:43.708 --> 02:44.875
Are you having fun?

02:46.208 --> 02:47.041
Yeah.

02:47.583 --> 02:49.333
My feet are soaked, but oh well.

02:51.791 --> 02:52.666
Mine are too.

02:54.125 --> 02:56.250
Some mountaineers we are.

02:56.333 --> 02:58.041
Hey, speak for yourself.

03:04.541 --> 03:05.500
Whoa!

03:06.666 --> 03:07.708
It was worth it.

03:09.958 --> 03:10.791
Yes.

03:12.541 --> 03:13.666
This is amazing.

03:18.916 --> 03:20.333
I'm going to take a picture.

03:31.291 --> 03:33.041
My fingers are freezing.

03:39.708 --> 03:40.958
It came out shitty.

03:42.583 --> 03:43.708
Doesn't do it justice.

03:44.208 --> 03:46.791
In that case,
you'll just have to remember it.

03:58.916 --> 04:02.708
-Look, how about here.
-It's too steep. I'm not sure about this.

04:03.333 --> 04:05.208
-Nico, are you scared?
-No.

04:05.291 --> 04:07.666
-But I'd like to live a few more years.
-Let's see.

04:07.750 --> 04:09.750
Come on. Hold on tight. Hold on.

04:10.541 --> 04:12.375
One, two…

04:14.458 --> 04:15.333
and three!

04:19.041 --> 04:19.875
Now.

04:22.958 --> 04:25.250
It's gaining speed! Hey!

04:26.833 --> 04:28.000
Stop! It won't stop!

04:44.000 --> 04:45.000
Lina?

04:46.333 --> 04:47.166
Lina?

04:47.791 --> 04:48.666
Are you okay?

04:49.458 --> 04:51.875
-It's like… My head hurts a lot.
-Where?

04:51.958 --> 04:53.250
Like…

04:53.833 --> 04:54.708
Like here!

04:55.291 --> 04:56.125
Damn you!

05:00.458 --> 05:01.291
Nico!

05:02.583 --> 05:03.708
I'll show you.

05:04.375 --> 05:05.208
Hey!

05:05.291 --> 05:07.541
-What? What now, huh?
-That's freezing! Stop!

05:15.541 --> 05:16.500
What?

05:17.333 --> 05:19.708
That's right, pal!

05:19.791 --> 05:20.625
Stop!

05:26.458 --> 05:28.208
-No!
-Now what?

05:28.708 --> 05:31.375
-Want some snow? A snow cocktail?
-I can't! No.

05:31.458 --> 05:32.291
Just a bit?

05:34.083 --> 05:35.250
Nico! Stop!

05:43.166 --> 05:44.458
You're such a traitor.

06:03.916 --> 06:04.875
This is so nice.

06:11.458 --> 06:13.041
I could stay like this forever.

06:14.458 --> 06:15.291
With you.

06:28.458 --> 06:29.333
Should we go?

06:30.708 --> 06:32.041
Come on, wait a second.

06:42.208 --> 06:44.041
I could also stay like this forever.

06:47.416 --> 06:50.166
But I don't have much of a choice.
I can't feel my feet.

06:51.708 --> 06:53.708
You might have to drag me to the cabin.

07:02.041 --> 07:03.083
I hurt my butt.

07:04.958 --> 07:07.958
-But I'm the one who ate all that snow.
-What did you expect?

07:35.416 --> 07:37.500
-What are you doing?
-Nothing.

07:38.625 --> 07:39.625
Play some music.

07:39.708 --> 07:41.250
Okay, but I'll play yours.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.083
I'm bored of mine.

07:48.708 --> 07:49.625
Ready?

07:50.666 --> 07:51.583
For what?

07:52.375 --> 07:53.250
A game.

07:56.708 --> 07:57.541
All right.

08:02.458 --> 08:03.333
Body parts.

08:04.208 --> 08:05.083
An action.

08:06.458 --> 08:07.291
All right.

08:07.833 --> 08:09.416
-I'll start.
-Okay.

08:10.916 --> 08:12.833
CARESS - KISS - LICK - BITE

08:12.916 --> 08:13.958
Caress

08:15.458 --> 08:16.291
butt.

08:20.250 --> 08:21.083
Go on.

08:22.875 --> 08:23.708
