08:29.291 --> 08:30.416
Go on, it's your turn.

08:55.375 --> 08:56.750
-Hey.
-What?

08:56.833 --> 08:58.333
It said kiss, not lick.

08:59.375 --> 09:00.500
You're a cheater.

09:01.375 --> 09:02.750
But you liked it, right?

09:09.208 --> 09:10.291
Second chance.

09:20.166 --> 09:22.083
I'm the sexiest guy in the Alps.

09:29.750 --> 09:30.833
Here goes

09:31.708 --> 09:32.791
a piece of my ass.

09:35.583 --> 09:38.541
Can you do it on the other side?
That's where I hurt myself.

09:39.291 --> 09:41.375
-You've got some nerve.
-Yeah.

09:51.166 --> 09:52.833
-Where did this come from?
-Well…

09:52.916 --> 09:55.458
-I'll skip it.
-No. Leave it.

09:55.541 --> 09:59.625
There's so much I want to tell you
There's so much I want

09:59.708 --> 10:00.958
Go on, spin it.

10:01.041 --> 10:02.541
To know about you

10:02.625 --> 10:05.916
We can start little by little

10:06.791 --> 10:10.916
Tell me why you're here

10:11.000 --> 10:14.708
Don't be afraid to tell me the truth

10:15.291 --> 10:18.958
